		<description><![CDATA[<p>=== In this lesson I'm going to show you one of (if not 'the') most important chord sequences I have ever learned. If you haven't noticed yet - most songs are built from the same types of chord movements... and...</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/bass-lines-grooves/the-ii-v-i-l196.html">One of the Most Important Chord Sequences You&#8217;ll Ever Learn &#8211; The II V I (L#196)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com">Online Bass Lessons</a>.</p>
